pageTitle: Itinerary for Tuesday, February 5, 2019 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Note: All times local

Ottawa, Ontario

9:30 a.m. The Prime Minister will attend the Cabinet meeting.

Note for media:

    • Ministers will be available to media in the third floor foyer of West Block as of 12:00 p.m.

2:00 p.m. The Prime Minister will attend Question Period.

4:15 p.m. The Prime Minister will meet with Premier of New Brunswick Blaine Higgs.

Room 215A
West Block
Parliament Hill

Note for media:

    • Photo opportunity at the beginning of the meeting
